cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and connection establishment issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting the global log level to an invalid value will cause logging configuration errors and prevent proper system monitoring.
du.explanation_zh: 將全域日誌級別設定為無效值會導致日誌配置錯誤，並阻止適當的系統監控。
